00:58:40,060 --> 00:58:43,060
 A friend...who's a girl. 

620
00:58:43,060 --> 00:58:46,190
 At that time, did you not have any girlfriends? 

621
00:58:46,190 --> 00:58:49,450
 Even now, I don't have one. 

